ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Citrix as a bad omen for LBOs</a=
>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The difficulties in executing Citrix=E2=80=99s=
 debt deal will likely make banks even more reluctant to underwrite large L=
BOs, investors said.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CBanks are in the moving business, not=
 the storage business,=E2=80=9D said Steven Hunter, chief executive at 9fin=
, a credit analytics platform. =E2=80=9CThey need to clear these deals in o=
rder to give them the capacity to underwrite new transactions.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you=E2=80=99re in the moving business and i=
t takes months to move, then you are also a little bit in the storage busin=
ess. If you keep buying inventory as the market goes up, you will lose mone=
y on your inventory when the market goes down.<a class=3D"footnote-index" h=
ref=3D"#footnote-3" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: i=
nline-block;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a>=C2=A0And probably stop buying so much inventory.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/29137297.267530/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQv=
ZGQzYTVkZWEtZWMwZC00NjU3LWI1MzYtOGFmNjg2ODdiZGFi/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB4=
