tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;"> the Financial Times on Citrix</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A hedge fund portfolio manager who reported be=
ing approached by Credit Suisse on the secured bond was surprised to hear f=
rom the lender.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIf they=E2=80=99re calling us to find=
 out what terms we would do on the secured bond deal, they=E2=80=99ve reall=
y gone down the list,=E2=80=9D the manager said, pointing out that the fund=
 does not typically operate in the high-yield credit space.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Might as well try everyone. Maybe the people w=
ho are not high-yield investors won=E2=80=99t notice that the high-yield ma=
rket has turned.</p>
