ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">options market</=
a>=C2=A0</em>really=C2=A0a paradise of transparency, competition and good e=
xecution for retail traders?) But payment for order flow gets the headlines=
.</p>
